==行為==
北方斑點鴞的地盤性極高。每一對都需要很大的地盤來築巢和獵食，除非因季節性的突然轉變，否則很少會離開地盤。它們具有獨特的飛行模式，包括一連串急速拍翼及滑翔飛行。它們可以寂靜的滑翔來捕捉獵物。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.defenders.org/wildlife_and_habitat/wildlife/spotted_owl,_northern.php|title=Northern Spotted Owl|publisher=Defenders of Wildlife|accessdate=2008-10-30|archive-date=2008-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081030003157/http://www.defenders.org/wildlife_and_habitat/wildlife/spotted_owl,_northern.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==繁殖==
北方斑點鴞到了2歲就可以[[繁殖|繁殖]]，不過一般要到3歲才開始。雄鳥及雌鳥會在2月或3月[[交配|交配]]，在3月或4月就會生2-3隻蛋。雌鳥會負擔孵蛋，孵化期約需30日。在孵化後，雛鳥會留在母鳥身邊8-10日，在34-36日大時就僧換羽。這段時間捕獵都是由雄鳥來負責。幼鳥會留在雙親身邊直至下一個[[夏天|夏天]]或[[秋天|秋天]]。到了[[冬天|冬天]]，幼鳥就會離巢自組家庭。[[春天|春天]]時，幼鳥的地盤與雙親的約相距38公里。<ref name="'brokaw'">{{cite news|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=s-cDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PT16&dq=Mother+Jones+Magazine+does+anybody+give+a+hoot%3F&hl=en&ei=1qFnTMyeOo2KvQPUqv39Aw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=Does anybody give a hoot?|last=Brokaw|first=Jeanne|date=Nov–Dec 1996|publisher=Mother Jones|page=15|accessdate=2010-08-15}}</ref>

==保育狀況==
現時野外約有3000-5000對北方斑點鴞，大部份都分佈在[[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]]、[[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]]及[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]。<ref name='csm'>{{cite news|author=Brad Knickerbocker|publisher=Christian Science Monitor|date=2007-06-27|title=Northern spotted owl's decline revives old concerns|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/2007/0627/p02s01-sten.html|accessdate=2007-06-27|archive-date=2007-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070629210930/http://www.csmonitor.com/2007/0627/p02s01-sten.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[加拿大|加拿大]]的群落只有少於100對；在[[英屬哥倫比亞|英屬哥倫比亞]]，野外就只餘下6對。<ref name='vansun'>{{cite news|author=Larry Pynn|publisher=The Vancouver Sun|date=March 24, 2010|title=Light dims on B.C.'s wild spotted owls}}</ref>

[[美國魚類暨野生動物局|美國魚類暨野生動物局]]於1982年及1987年檢討了北方斑點鴞的狀況，發覺並非處於瀕危。但到了1990年，北方斑點鴞卻被列入[[瀕危物種|瀕危物種]]中，最主要原因是失去了古老原始林的棲息地。<ref>Federal register 55 FR 26114-26194. [http://www.fws.gov/pacific/ecoservices/endangered/recovery/pdf/NSO_5-yr_Summary.pdf  Northern Spotted Owl Five-year Review] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fws.gov/pacific/ecoservices/endangered/recovery/pdf/NSO_5-yr_Summary.pdf |date=20121111073551 }} at U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service.</ref>美國亦已禁止在國家森林內伐林。<ref name="'brokaw'"/>2004年，局方再度確認它們處於瀕危，但成因卻改變了，而是[[橫斑林鴞|橫斑林鴞]]的入侵所致。<ref>{{Cite web|author=Hal Bernton|title=Northern spotted owl faces nonlogging threats|url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/localnews/2001962902_spottedowl23m.html|date=2004-06-23|publisher=The Seattle Times|accessdate=2011-01-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060210160351/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/localnews/2001962902_spottedowl23m.html|archivedate=2006-02-10}}</ref>

